More accurate delivery times, especially when faster, typically lead to better conversion rates. When the item updates are off, items with mismatched data aren't shown. This field is only updated (cleared) if provided.

The date is relative to the Proleptic Gregorian Calendar. If year, month, or day are 0, the DateTime is considered not to have a specific year, month, or day respectively.
